    <h4 class="odd">OPERATING INSTRUCTIONS</h4>

    This module and its operations are very simple:<br> <br>
    <ul>
        <li> Configure your preferences (e.g. select the text editor</li>
        <li>Add a Marquee</li>
        <li>Select a block you want this Marquee to be visible and set desired
            options
        </li>
        <li>Check that you have given your user groups the necessary module and
            block access rights to use this module. Group permissions are set through
            the Administration Menu -> System -> Groups.
        </li>
    </ul>
